"Lynce": "Are you an ARKS from the Aelio Region?"
"We're short on manpower right now, so I have a favor to ask you. Is that alright?"

"Oh. Well, that's too bad...
Maybe another time."
"I'd like you to go and get some Tames meat. Some good meat should help everyone recover sooner."
"I know I'm asking a lot, but we really need this. Take care of yourself out there."
"Thank you. That should be more than enough to turn into a healthy, nutritious meal."
"I'm sorry to pile even more on you, but could you hand them over to Marlynn?"
